ResponseMessages.QuickReplyTitle: After logging in, you can start the discussion by clicking the corresponding button on the homepage. It is a post published on RoundTable for asking questions or exchanging opinions. You can ask open questions, technical questions, etc.

To modify or edit a discussion post, you need to first click the three dots in the upper right corner of the corresponding discussion post, and then click the update button to confirm your action after completing the modification.
To delete or remove your discussion posts, first, you need to navigate to your profile and view the discussion posts you have published and deleted from here.

ResponseMessages.QuickReplyTitle: It is very easy to bookmark discussion posts. You just need to click the bookmark icon on the corresponding discussion that you want to save for future reference.
In order to delete a bookmark, you need to go to the bookmarks section and click the three dots in the upper right corner of the bookmark, just like deleting a discussion post.

Sharing is caring! You can invite your friends to participate in the discussion through various methods (such as URL or embed code) by clicking the three dots in the upper right corner of the bookmark.
